 and work, but also the examination of today's perspectives and future work in the field of infectious and "neglected" diseases. The authors address current scientific information on the relevant bacteria Bartonella bacilliformis, besides current research and clinical status of the other Bartonellas, making it a useful and practical text for those studying infectious diseases.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aBartonella infections. 0aMedicinezPeruxHistoryy19th century. 0aMedicinezPeruxHistoryy20th century. 7aMEDICAL / General.2bisacsh  aPeru, Peruvian Central Railway, Lima, La Oroya, Oroya Fever, medicine, Alberto Leonardo Barton, Andean valley, Peruvian Verruga, Verruca, Berruga, Daniel A. Carrion, disease, science, Richard Strong, Bartonella bacillifornis.1 aAlarcón, Graciela S., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAlarcón, Renato D, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aAlarcón, Renato D., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCáceres, Uriel García, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCáceres, Uriel García.1 aGonzales, Rolly Barton.1 aMaguiña, Ciro, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMaguiña, Ciro.1 aUgarte-Gil, César, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aUgarte-Gil, César.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2019 Englishz978311061053608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2019z9783110606386oZDB-23-DPM08iTit